---
// AuditTimeline.astro — Pure CSS visual timeline of agent reasoning
// Shows each step as a colored node on a vertical timeline
---

<div class="tl-wrap">
  <h3 class="tl-title">Inside One Agent Check</h3>
  <p class="tl-sub">Every thought, tool call, and decision — visible and traceable.</p>

  <div class="timeline">
    <div class="tl-line" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="tl-step tl-step--amber" style="--delay: 0.1s">
      <div class="tl-dot tl-dot--amber"></div>
      <div class="tl-card">
        <div class="tl-head">
          <span class="tl-tag tl-tag--amber">THINK</span>
          <span class="tl-agent">Orchestrator</span>
          <span class="tl-ts">00:00.12</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tl-body">Received ORDER-A7. Breaking it down: check the value → look up the rule → verify the limit.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tl-step tl-step--cyan" style="--delay: 0.2s">
      <div class="tl-dot tl-dot--cyan"></div>
      <div class="tl-card">
        <div class="tl-head">
          <span class="tl-tag tl-tag--cyan">TOOL</span>
          <span class="tl-agent">Data Checker</span>
          <span class="tl-ts">00:00.34</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tl-body">
          <code>check_value(item="ORDER-A7", field="discount", limit=20)</code>
          <div class="tl-result tl-result--red">→ EXCEEDED: discount is 35% (max allowed: 20%)</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tl-step tl-step--amber" style="--delay: 0.3s">
      <div class="tl-dot tl-dot--amber"></div>
      <div class="tl-card">
        <div class="tl-head">
          <span class="tl-tag tl-tag--amber">THINK</span>
          <span class="tl-agent">Orchestrator</span>
          <span class="tl-ts">00:00.41</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tl-body">Problem found. Need to find the exact rule before flagging. Searching the rule database.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tl-step tl-step--cyan" style="--delay: 0.4s">
      <div class="tl-dot tl-dot--cyan"></div>
      <div class="tl-card">
        <div class="tl-head">
          <span class="tl-tag tl-tag--cyan">TOOL</span>
          <span class="tl-agent">Vector Search</span>
          <span class="tl-ts">00:00.58</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tl-body">
          <code>search_rules("discount limit policy")</code>
          <div class="tl-result tl-result--blue">→ Rule §3.1: "Max discount for standard orders is 20%"</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tl-step tl-step--amber" style="--delay: 0.5s">
      <div class="tl-dot tl-dot--amber"></div>
      <div class="tl-card">
        <div class="tl-head">
          <span class="tl-tag tl-tag--amber">THINK</span>
          <span class="tl-agent">Orchestrator</span>
          <span class="tl-ts">00:00.65</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tl-body">Rule found: §3.1. Violation confirmed: 35% &gt; 20% max. Citing the rule in the flag.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tl-step tl-step--green" style="--delay: 0.6s">
      <div class="tl-dot tl-dot--green"></div>
      <div class="tl-card tl-card--highlight">
        <div class="tl-head">
          <span class="tl-tag tl-tag--green">LOG</span>
          <span class="tl-agent">Decision Logger</span>
          <span class="tl-ts">00:00.72</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tl-body">
          <div class="tl-flag">
            <div class="tl-flag-row"><span class="tl-flag-key">Record:</span> ORDER-A7</div>
            <div class="tl-flag-row"><span class="tl-flag-key">Issue:</span> §3.1 — Discount 35% (max: 20%)</div>
            <div class="tl-flag-row"><span class="tl-flag-key">Confidence:</span> 97%</div>
            <div class="tl-flag-row"><span class="tl-flag-key">Rule Cited:</span> <span class="tl-flag-yes">✓ Yes</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="tl-insight">
    <div class="tl-insight-icon">📋</div>
    <div>This is what makes it trustworthy. Not a black box — a <strong>glass box</strong>. Every step is traceable and explainable.</div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .tl-wrap {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    border: 1px solid #334155;
  }
  .tl-title { color: #f1f5f9; font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 0.25rem; }
  .tl-sub { color: #64748b; font-size: 0.8rem; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; font-family: monospace; }

  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 28px;
  }
  .tl-line {
    position: absolute;
    left: 9px;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f59e0b40, #06b6d440, #4ade8040);
  }

  .tl-step {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    animation: tl-fade-in 0.5s ease-out both;
    animation-delay: var(--delay, 0s);
  }
  @keyframes tl-fade-in {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-8px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
  }

  .tl-dot {
    position: absolute;
    left: -24px;
    top: 12px;
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .tl-dot--amber { background: #f59e0b; box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(245,158,11,0.4); }
  .tl-dot--cyan  { background: #06b6d4; box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(6,182,212,0.4); }
  .tl-dot--green { background: #4ade80; box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(74,222,128,0.4); }

  .tl-card {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
    border: 1px solid #334155;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }
  .tl-step--amber .tl-card:hover { border-color: #f59e0b30; }
  .tl-step--cyan .tl-card:hover  { border-color: #06b6d430; }
  .tl-step--green .tl-card:hover { border-color: #4ade8030; }
  .tl-card--highlight {
    background: rgba(74,222,128,0.04);
    border-color: #4ade8030;
  }

  .tl-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .tl-tag {
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    padding: 2px 7px;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .tl-tag--amber { background: rgba(245,158,11,0.12); color: #f59e0b; }
  .tl-tag--cyan  { background: rgba(6,182,212,0.12); color: #06b6d4; }
  .tl-tag--green { background: rgba(74,222,128,0.12); color: #4ade80; }

  .tl-agent { font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.6rem; color: #64748b; }
  .tl-ts { font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.55rem; color: #475569; margin-left: auto; }

  .tl-body {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #94a3b8;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .tl-body code {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: #67e8f9;
    background: rgba(6,182,212,0.06);
    padding: 4px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    font-family: monospace;
  }
  .tl-result {
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding-top: 2px;
  }
  .tl-result--red { color: #f87171; }
  .tl-result--blue { color: #60a5fa; }

  .tl-flag {
    background: rgba(74,222,128,0.04);
    border: 1px dashed #4ade8030;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 8px 10px;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .tl-flag-row {
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: #94a3b8;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .tl-flag-key { color: #64748b; }
  .tl-flag-yes { color: #4ade80; font-weight: 700; }

  .tl-insight {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 16px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    background: rgba(74,222,128,0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(74,222,128,0.15);
    border-radius: 10px;
    color: #cbd5e1;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .tl-insight strong { color: #4ade80; }
  .tl-insight-icon { font-size: 1.1rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
</style>
